===Etymology===
From the name of the town of its discovery, [[w:Darmstadt|Darmstadt]].

===Noun===
'''darmstadtium''' ([[w:Darmstadtium|Wikipedia:Darmstadtium]])

# the 110th [[element]] in the [[periodic table]], formerly known as [[Ununnilium]].  Its symbol is [[Ds]].

